test.name: 1. Login as Employer. And click 'Post a Job'.
3. Login as FL. Go to Find Jobs page.
4. Login as EMP. And Hire the FL
5. Login as FL. Accept job on Dashboard. Fill agreement details
6. Preview Agreement, and send to employer. Log out.
7. Login as Emp, and verify agreement pending alert is shown.
8. Click on Agreement Pending, and verify 'Accept' and 'Decline' buttons are shown. Click Accept, and accept the agreement.
9. Login as FL, and click on the Job link, and go to Workroom. Navigate to Agreement and Click on Edit. Click Cancel.
9. Click Edit and then click X icon.
10. Click Edit and then click Continue button. Verify Revise Agreement page. Revise agreement to Hourly, enter details, and send to emp.
11. Login as Emp and decline agreement.
